            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Memex alpha build 9</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Retires the Web, Raycast, and legacy memory surfaces from the packaged app path.</li>
  <li>Keeps the macOS bundle focused on the native helper, bundled core, and tracked config only.</li>
  <li>Verifies the packaged bundle audit still excludes runtime, artifact, and legacy adapter paths.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
