        <item>
            <title>0.0.0-dev</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 21:18:37 +0800</pubDate>
            <sparkle:channel>alpha</sparkle:channel>
            <sparkle:version>8</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.0.0-dev</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Memex alpha build 8</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Moves alpha/dev OpenAI key storage off macOS Keychain to avoid ad-hoc update ACL prompts.</li>
  <li>Keeps release builds on Keychain storage.</li>
  <li>Fails opted-in sends clearly when no local OpenAI key is saved, instead of falling back to mock.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
