            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Memex alpha build 6</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Stops startup and Settings diagnostics from reading Keychain.</li>
  <li>Keeps OpenAI key migration for normal incremental updates.</li>
  <li>Reads the saved key only when saving or replacing it, or when an opted-in OpenAI send needs it.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
